Ramhorn:


Ramhorn got up slightly.  He could feel himself slipping away.  He would be 
nothing but a mindless shell in a few minutes or so.  Seeing Dark Mouse being 
taken away by one hella ugly Predacon he slammed a fist on the ground.  
"Ramulus...save...mouse!" he yelled, barely able to form words.  Raising his 
rifle, he fired off twenty sonic shells off, fifteen at the back of 
Quickstrike's legs, five at the back of Double Punch's, Double Punch 
stumbling and falling over.
